voice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-001-26"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So, what was it that you did@back there?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200900,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-001-28"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Um, I don't really understand it@either, but..."},{"chara":[{"id":200900,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-001-29"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]When I looked into your eyes, a scene@just started playing out in my head..."},{"chara":[{"id":200900,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-001-30"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Almost like screening a film..."},{"chara":[{"id":200900,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-001-31"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]In it, I saw myself giving directions@to you as you fought."},{"chara":[{"id":200900,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-001-32"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]And when I did the same thing@in reality, everything played out@just like it did in the film."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200900,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913004-001-33"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Could this be...the power of my magic?"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"deleteArmatureList":[1],"surround":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
